291
00:16:18,599 --> 00:16:19,359
No idea.

292
00:16:30,280 --> 00:16:33,359
-Lin Xi, out for morning exercise?
-Yeah.

293
00:16:39,840 --> 00:16:43,679
Well, Lin Xi, I was wondering...

294
00:16:43,960 --> 00:16:47,080
You and Jiang Zheng Han

295
00:16:47,080 --> 00:16:49,960
