351
00:20:32,719 --> 00:20:34,199
Medicinal herbs? Let me have a look.

352
00:20:35,119 --> 00:20:36,040
Gee!

353
00:20:36,040 --> 00:20:38,319
Lin Xi, it's overcooked.

354
00:20:38,319 --> 00:20:39,319
Overcooked?!

355
00:20:40,599 --> 00:20:42,920
So, is this still edible?

356
00:20:43,199 --> 00:20:44,400
