What should I do now?

359
00:20:55,880 --> 00:20:57,079
Alas!

360
00:20:57,079 --> 00:20:59,199
Lin Xi. Lin Xi!

361
00:20:59,439 --> 00:20:59,680
What?

362
00:21:02,520 --> 00:21:03,280
This porridge

363
