not the taste.

364
00:21:06,000 --> 00:21:08,160
Take my word for it.

365
00:21:08,680 --> 00:21:08,839
Okay?

366
00:21:30,880 --> 00:21:34,040
I really want to see
whether that person can

367
00:21:34,119 --> 00:21:36,199
drink up your overcooked porridge or not.

368
00:21:38,040 --> 00:21:40,640
Didn't you say that
my intention matters the most?

369
00:21:40,640 --> 00:21:41,880
Then don't give it away.

370
00:21:44,719 --> 00:21:48,800
It's such a pity that
I missed a big show yesterday.

371
00:21:51,239 --> 00:21:51,479
Hey.

372
00:21:52,880 --> 00:21:54,400
If someone drank for me,

373
00:21:54,400 --> 00:21:56,680
I would also care about him by all means.

374
00:21:56,680 --> 00:21:58,199
That's normal politeness.

375
00:21:59,160 --> 00:22:02,079
But if you always keep it a secret,

376
00:22:02,640 --> 00:22:04,280
that's a problem.

377
00:22:06,239 --> 00:22:07,719
