378
00:22:08,839 --> 00:22:12,239
-Lots of people knew it.
-Lots of people?!

379
00:22:13,000 --> 00:22:14,079
Really so many people?

380
00:22:16,359 --> 00:22:17,839
I think he's pretty good.

381
00:22:18,839 --> 00:22:19,199
Okay...

382
00:22:21,079 --> 00:22:23,800
Alright, he's definitely not
feeling well today.

383
00:22:23,839 --> 00:22:25,280
Go and give your porridge to him.

384
00:22:25,280 --> 00:22:26,359
I'll hold the seat for you.

385
00:22:29,439 --> 00:22:31,959
Then I'm leaving.

386
00:22:31,959 --> 00:22:33,280
Quickly go!

387
00:22:39,239 --> 00:22:40,239
What are you doing?

388
00:22:40,560 --> 00:22:41,719
Turn around.

389
00:22:42,239 --> 00:22:44,439
Oh, here comes Jiang Zheng Han.

390
00:22:44,760 --> 00:22:46,719
Quickly give it to him. Go!

391
00:22:47,439 --> 00:22:48,359
Wait for a while.

392
00:22:48,560 --> 00:22:48,920
I...

393
00:22:49,079 --> 00:22:49,439
I...

394
00:22:49,959 --> 00:22:51,359
I'm not ready yet.

395
00:22:56,280 --> 00:22:58,319
-Hey, there he is.
-Hey, let's go.

396
00:22:58,880 --> 00:23:00,199
I'll do it later.

397
00:23:00,920 --> 00:23:02,959
Oh, no. He got company.

398
00:23:03,680 --> 00:23:04,560
Is your stomach still aching?

399
00:23:05,119 --> 00:23:06,959
You were not there yesterday.
What happened?

400
00:23:06,959 --> 00:23:08,599
-How much have you drunk?
-Not much.

401
00:23:10,160 --> 00:23:10,680
Homework.

402
00:23:11,880 --> 00:23:12,959
Here you go.

403
00:23:13,520 --> 00:23:16,719
Help us with the questions
and the formula writing.

404
00:23:17,239 --> 00:23:18,079
Old rules, two hundred yuan.

405
00:23:18,439 --> 00:23:20,280
Professor Shi urges it.
Another fifty yuan.

406
00:23:20,280 --> 00:23:22,079
Money, we don't have that much.

407
00:23:22,079 --> 00:23:24,119
But there are consolations.

408
00:23:24,119 --> 00:23:25,239
Hello, everybody.

409
00:23:25,239 --> 00:23:26,959
Give him what you've prepared.

410
00:23:27,090 --> 00:23:28,600
-Come, come.
-Hurry, hurry.

411
00:23:30,520 --> 00:23:32,160
Jiang, you gotta get better soon.

412
00:23:32,160 --> 00:23:34,400
-We're expecting your contest.
-That's right.

413
00:23:34,520 --> 00:23:36,880
Gosh. Lin Xi.

414
00:23:36,880 --> 00:23:39,560
You've got too many allies.

415
00:23:41,000 --> 00:23:43,319
You're the light of our computer dept.
You can't fall ill.

416
00:23:43,319 --> 00:23:44,680
Yeah. That's right, Jiang.

417
00:23:44,680 --> 00:23:46,280
Take some medicine for your hangover.

418
00:23:47,599 --> 00:23:48,359
What's going on?

419
00:23:48,839 --> 00:23:51,400
Didn't you defeat that notorious stirrer
of our university by drinking yesterday?

420
00:23:51,400 --> 00:23:54,560
It's said that all the clubs
have been troubled by He Guang Yu.

421
00:23:54,680 --> 00:23:56,439
So they're all here for you.

422
00:23:57,079 --> 00:23:57,640
Well...

423
00:23:58,520 --> 00:24:00,680
They came to me early in the morning,
asking which class you're gonna have.

424
00:24:00,839 --> 00:24:02,359
The point is, I'm not used to this.

425
00:24:02,719 --> 00:24:04,239
-I'm leaving.
-No, no, no.

426
00:24:04,239 --> 00:24:06,839
Well, thank you for your concern.

427
00:24:06,839 --> 00:24:09,479
I'm not feeling well.
I'm going to the hospital.

428
00:24:09,560 --> 00:24:10,920
These two guys will keep your gifts.

429
00:24:10,920 --> 00:24:12,599
Thanks for your kindness. Thank you.

430
00:24:12,599 --> 00:24:13,040
Well, this...

431
00:24:13,719 --> 00:24:15,599
-Talent Jiang, don't go.
-Thank you, senior.

432
00:24:16,160 --> 00:24:17,239
Thank you. Thank you.

433
00:24:17,839 --> 00:24:20,160
-We keep your gifts for him first.
-Thank you.

434
00:24:20,359 --> 00:24:21,359
Thank you.

435
00:24:21,760 --> 00:24:23,479
Oh, no, he starts looking this way.

436
00:24:23,800 --> 00:24:24,760
Put it here. Put it here.

437
00:24:27,400 --> 00:24:28,000
Lin Xi.

438
00:24:29,680 --> 00:24:30,800
-Lin Xi.
-Um?

439
00:24:31,199 --> 00:24:32,000
You're here.

440
00:24:32,640 --> 00:24:34,880
Yeah, I'm in class. What's up?

441
00:24:40,160 --> 00:24:40,959
This is...

442
00:24:53,040 --> 00:24:53,839
Thank you.

443
00:24:56,599 --> 00:24:59,199
-Look, what is Zheng doing?
-Go. Go. Go.

444
