Zheng.

445
00:25:13,959 --> 00:25:16,000
-This porridge is overcooked.
-Overcooked? Let me see it.

446
00:25:16,479 --> 00:25:16,959
Don't...

447
00:25:19,800 --> 00:25:22,800
Got it. Something from his girlfriend
cannot be touched.

448
00:25:22,880 --> 00:25:25,079
It's not like what we bachelors gave.

449
00:25:25,079 --> 00:25:27,760
