452
00:25:31,400 --> 00:25:32,800
Oh, love...

453
00:25:32,800 --> 00:25:34,199
It makes him beyond recognition.

454
00:25:34,199 --> 00:25:35,680
Go. Go. Go. Go away.

455
00:25:35,680 --> 00:25:37,160
You're particular about wording with me?

456
00:25:37,160 --> 00:25:38,439
Don't you see what is it?

457
00:25:38,719 --> 00:25:40,560
The gift from his beloved girl

458
00:25:40,560 --> 00:25:42,199
