468
00:25:54,959 --> 00:25:55,520
Right.

469
00:25:55,920 --> 00:25:58,000
He does get his mouth full of
this loving porridge.

470
00:25:58,000 --> 00:25:58,280
Yeah.

471
00:25:58,680 --> 00:26:01,040
But we can't do nothing about it.

472
00:26:01,119 --> 00:26:02,160
We have to prepare a big gift

473
00:26:02,479 --> 00:26:03,920
for him.

474
00:26:04,599 --> 00:26:05,599
Yeah.

475
00:26:07,079 --> 00:26:08,400
What do you want to do?

476
00:26:08,400 --> 00:26:09,280
You know me.

477
00:26:09,280 --> 00:26:10,520
-Oh, no, no, no.
-No, no, I...

478
00:26:10,920 --> 00:26:12,199
Zheng, you can count on us.

479
00:26:12,199 --> 00:26:13,959
No, don't go too far.

480
00:26:14,479 --> 00:26:15,479
Don't worry.

481
00:26:15,479 --> 00:26:16,479
Leave it to us.

482
00:26:16,479 --> 00:26:16,680
Huh?

483
00:26:17,239 --> 00:26:18,920
-Listen, this is what we have to do.
-No, listen to me...

484
00:26:19,400 --> 00:26:20,359
No, listen to me.

485
00:26:20,359 --> 00:26:21,439
Oh, stop it.

486
00:26:21,880 --> 00:26:25,800
Hey, Chen Yi Chuan, listen,
don't look down upon me.

487
00:26:25,880 --> 00:26:27,000
When you fall in love,

488
00:26:27,000 --> 00:26:29,239
there will be times for you
to beg me on your knees.

489
00:26:29,359 --> 00:26:31,959
Beg you? I prefer to give you a punch.

490
00:26:32,119 --> 00:26:34,000
