491
00:26:34,000 --> 00:26:34,439
Hey!

492
00:26:34,680 --> 00:26:37,040
-Oh, listen to me. Do as I say .
-You listen to me.

493
00:26:37,040 --> 00:26:37,479
Yo!

494
00:26:38,040 --> 00:26:39,160
-Hello, senior.
-Hello, senior.

495
00:26:39,160 --> 00:26:40,000
-Hey.
-Hello.

496
00:26:40,199 --> 00:26:40,800
Look. Look.

497
00:26:40,800 --> 00:26:42,119
