500
00:26:45,959 --> 00:26:46,719
Jiang Zheng Han.

501
00:26:46,719 --> 00:26:47,119
Alas!

502
00:26:48,319 --> 00:26:50,280
You can eat it
even though it's overcooked?

503
00:26:50,560 --> 00:26:51,400
None of your business.

504
00:26:51,719 --> 00:26:54,359
