508
00:27:02,760 --> 00:27:04,560
Tell you what, I got it right away.

509
00:27:04,560 --> 00:27:05,439
-Yeah!
-Yeah!

510
00:27:05,520 --> 00:27:06,239
Tell us.

511
00:27:07,280 --> 00:27:10,359
What kind of goddess she is? Of what type?

512
00:27:10,560 --> 00:27:11,680
How come she gave Zheng

513
00:27:11,680 --> 00:27:13,479
